# 🚦 Road Accident Analysis Dashboard

## 📌 Project Overview

This project analyzes road accident data to identify patterns, trends, and key factors contributing to accidents. The dashboard provides interactive visualizations that help stakeholders understand accident severity, casualty distribution, vehicle involvement, location analysis, and time-based trends.

The project demonstrates practical Data Analytics skills using Excel and dashboard development techniques.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

- Analyze road accident data.
- Identify accident trends and patterns.
- Compare casualties by vehicle type.
- Understand accident severity distribution.
- Analyze accidents by road type, location, and weather conditions.
- Build an interactive dashboard for decision-making.

---

## 🛠️ Tools Used

- Microsoft Excel
- Pivot Tables
- Pivot Charts
- Slicers
- Conditional Formatting
- Data Cleaning
- Dashboard Design

---

## 📊 Dashboard Features

- Total Casualties
- Total Accidents
- Fatal Casualties
- Serious Casualties
- Slight Casualties
- Casualties by Vehicle Type
- Monthly Accident Trend
- Road Type Analysis
- Urban vs Rural Comparison
- Day vs Night Analysis
- Interactive Filters (Slicers)

