## 🚀 How to Use

1. Download the project files from the Google Drive link.
2. Open the Excel workbook.
3. Enable editing if prompted.
4. Use the slicers to interact with the dashboard.
5. Explore different accident insights.

---

## 📈 Key Insights

- Majority of casualties are classified as Slight.
- Cars contribute to the highest number of casualties.
- Urban areas record more accidents than rural areas.
- Road type significantly affects accident frequency.
- Monthly trends help identify seasonal accident patterns.

